(109, 1, '2012-10-06 10:42:44', '2012-10-06 10:42:44', '<p>I chose to create a Holmfirth Website because I lived in Holmfirth for about 10 years.  I knew the community and the people.  The reason for this was my final year project at university.  We had to chose a project we were interested in, I decided to investigate whether a website could bring a community together.  I ended up with an A for it, so all the hard work I put it was worth it in the end.</p>\n<p>The website design was created to give a feel of togetherness.  I wanted neighbours to bump into each other since they no longer were doing this by not walking to the local shop, but by driving out of town, etc.  So I created a forum, and added a section where community members could add events and invite others to them.  I also published latest comments and forum posts, members who had joined, etc, in the sidebar, so neighbours could instead <em>virtually</em> bump into each other.</p>', 'Holmfirth Community Project', '', 'draft', 'open', 'closed', '', 'holmfirth-website', '', '', '2012-10-06 10:42:44', '2012-10-06 10:42:44', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=websites&amp;p=109', 15, 'website', '', 0),
(110, 1, '2012-10-05 16:09:26', '2012-10-05 16:09:26', 'That''s ok.  I can meet up with you and discuss the look you want, maybe design it around your current logo, or letterhead.  Have a look at the <a title="Mirfield Heating Engineering Company" href="http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/projects/a-mirfield-websit-engineering-company/">website I created for plg-engineering</a>.  All they had was a logo, I designed the website based on the colour scheme in that logo.  If you don''t have a logo or letterhead, that''s something that Huddersfield Website Design can do as well.  David Speight Photography and Lifting Inspection Services didn''t have a logo or any other branding, their logo was developed based on the type of product they were offering and the audience is was aimed at.', 'I need a website but I''m not sure what it should look like', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'i-need-a-website-but-im-not-sure-what-it-should-look-like', '', '', '2012-10-05 16:09:26', '2012-10-05 16:09:26', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=faq&amp;p=46', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
(111, 1, '2012-10-05 16:56:54', '2012-10-05 16:56:54', 'I cannot guarantee your site will be top in google.  However, I do follow all the guidelines Google provide to ensure that your site has the best chance of climbing the rankings in a google search.  The best way of achieving this is by identifying what keywords you wish to target and then optimising your content for these keywords.  Google provide a really helpful video at <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=El3IZFGERbM&amp;feature=share" target="_blank">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=El3IZFGERbM&amp;feature=share</a>', 'What about optimising the site so it appears top in Google?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'what-about-optimising-the-site-so-it-appears-top-in-google', '', '', '2012-10-05 16:56:54', '2012-10-05 16:56:54', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=faq&amp;p=49', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
(112, 1, '2012-10-05 17:10:58', '2012-10-05 17:10:58', '<p>Hosting simply refers to where the files that make up your website live.  You can arrange your website hosting yourself, there are numerous providers out there, and provide me with the details, or I can set all that up for you, choosing a hosting provider on your behalf and adding the cost to the bill.  Typically, the cost is around £30 - £70 a year ,the cost depending on who you go with, and which package you choose.  I always recommend <a title="tsohosts" href="http://my.tsohost.com/aff.php?aff=1873" target="_blank">tsohost</a> to my clients.  I find them reliable and very quick to respond to any support issues.</p>', 'What about hosting?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'what-about-hosting', '', '', '2012-10-05 17:10:58', '2012-10-05 17:10:58', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=faq&amp;p=54', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
(113, 1, '2012-10-05 17:14:01', '2012-10-05 17:14:01', 'A domain name is the web address where your website lives.  e.g. google.com, or bbc.co.uk.  Every website needs a domain.  Which name you choose depends on a few things such as :\n<ul>\n	<li>what is available (i.e. no one else has bought it),</li>\n	<li>whether you want a .com or .co.uk address</li>\n	<li>if you want it to be the same as your company name</li>\n	<li>whether you want it to be easy to remember or spell</li>\n</ul>\nTo check if the domain name is available go to <a href="http://www.123-reg.co.uk/" target="_blank">123-reg.co.uk</a> and about halfway down the page there is a box you can put in your desired domain name to search to see if it''s available.  Domain names typically cost about £8 for the .co.uk extension, .com domains can be a little bit more, starting from around £20.\n\nI can sort the purchasing of the domain name out and just add it to the invoice as a disbursement.', 'Do I need a domain name?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'do-i-need-a-domain-name', '', '', '2012-10-05 17:14:01', '2012-10-05 17:14:01', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=faq&amp;p=56', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
(114, 1, '2013-04-05 17:22:51', '2013-04-05 17:22:51', '<p>It depends on how complicated your site is.  I charge based on how much time I estimate it will take me.  A typical website will cost between £500 and £1,000.  I will discuss this with you before undertaking any work, and then send you a quotation for approval.  If you are happy with that, I simply ask for 25% of the total upfront to cover any disbursements I may have to make, and as a token of your commitment.</p>', 'How much do you charge?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'how-much-do-you-charge', '', '', '2013-04-05 17:22:51', '2013-04-05 17:22:51', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=faq&amp;p=59', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
(115, 1, '2012-10-05 17:26:32', '2012-10-05 17:26:32', 'I can do this using wordpress.  It is then very straightforward for you to simply add your products to wordpress.  I can customise the product screen so you can have whatever fields are suitable for you, e.g. image, size, colour etc.  You will need to make sure you have a paypal account.  Have a look at <a title="Photography E-Commerce Site" href="http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/projects/photography-e-commerce-site/">this e-commerce site I did for a local photographer</a> as an example.', 'Can you do an e-commerce website with a shopping cart?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'can-you-do-an-e-commerce-website-with-a-shopping-cart', '', '', '2012-10-05 17:26:32', '2012-10-05 17:26:32', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=faq&amp;p=62', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
(116, 1, '2013-04-04 17:28:14', '2013-04-04 17:28:14', '<p>It depends on whether I have any other projects on at the moment.  As I work full time, I can only work on one project at a time.  However, it would usually be between 2 - 8 weeks from the date we meet to discuss your requirements.</p>', 'How long will it take?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'how-long-will-it-take', '', '', '2013-04-04 17:28:14', '2013-04-04 17:28:14', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=faq&amp;p=64', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
(117, 1, '2012-10-05 17:29:37', '2012-10-05 17:29:37', 'No, I do website for anyone in any area. I simply call myself Huddersfield Web Design because I live in Huddersfield and know the area.  I have made websites for clients in Halifax, Batley, Cleckheaton, Mirfield, and Manchester.', 'Do you only do websites in Huddersfield?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'do-you-only-do-websites-in-huddersfield', '', '', '2012-10-05 17:29:37', '2012-10-05 17:29:37', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=faq&amp;p=66', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
(118, 1, '2012-10-05 17:32:12', '2012-10-05 17:32:12', 'I do.  If you are for instance a designer by trade, you can do the design yourself and I can just create the website.  However, usually, clients like me to do the design and build of the site.', 'Do you design and build the website?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'do-you-do-the-design-and-the-building-of-the-website', '', '', '2012-10-05 17:32:12', '2012-10-05 17:32:12', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=faq&amp;p=68', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
(119, 1, '2012-10-05 17:34:51', '2012-10-05 17:34:51', 'I can do this alongside creating your website, or I can do this as a project on it''s own.  It is important to have a consistent brand across different mediums.  You want your business cards to reflect the design on your website to reinforce the brand identity.', 'Can you create me a logo and some business cards?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'can-you-create-me-a-logo-and-some-business-cards', '', '', '2012-10-05 17:34:51', '2012-10-05 17:34:51', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=faq&amp;p=70', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
