(138, 1, '2012-10-06 19:52:08', '2012-10-06 19:52:08', 'This was my own portfolio website I created just before starting my final year at university.  I wanted the website to reflect my own personality, which is why I decided upon a hand-drawn design, I am very artistic and creative and I feel this represented me very well.  The backdrop was to mimic a natural fabric, again reinforcing the organic feeling of the website.\n\nOn  seeing the site for the first time, one of my friends commented how it didn''t seem like a website, but like something away from a computer.  That made my day because that was exactly what I wanted to achieve.  I built the site in php and created a content management system for myself to add new projects easily to it.  The site also features a twitter feed from my twitter account.', 'Personal Portfolio Website', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'personal-portfolio-website', '', '', '2018-03-15 18:05:47', '2018-03-15 18:05:47', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=websites&#038;p=138', 4, 'website', '', 0),
