(146, 1, '2012-10-06 15:04:09', '2012-10-06 15:04:09', 'This Bradford Website was created during my time at Bradford Royal Infirmary as a placement student.  The hospital wanted to let the public know what it''s plans were for a new ward block on the site.  My task was to create a simple yet appealing website showcasing the 3D designs of what the intended new wards would look like.  The design was integrated with Bradford Royal Infirmary''s branding, which was the purple.  It is very simple and effective.  When the website was first launched, it featured a survey on it asking members of the public to indicate which ward they would like to be housed in the new building.\n\nThe public responded very positively to the design and commented that it had helped them view the options available to them as foundation trust members.', 'Public Information Bradford Website at BRI', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bradford-website-at-bri', '', '', '2018-03-15 18:05:56', '2018-03-15 18:05:56', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=websites&#038;p=146', 25, 'website', '', 0),
