(155, 1, '2012-03-06 15:20:37', '2012-03-06 15:20:37', 'This project was an interesting one.  It was one of my very first freelance jobs.  My client wanted a logo creating which he wanted on his website.  He then needed for a flyer, some business cards designed and a letterhead.  I created the logo based of the nature of the company.  They inspected lifting equipment, such as cranes used in theatre productions etc.  With this in mind I created a logo showing a crane lifting the company name.  Scroll down to see it.\n\nThis logo was then adapted onto various mediums.  The flyer was created to inform people that they had to comply to certain safety standards if they were using lifting equipment.  The flyer needed to bold and in your face, it needed to stand out, whilst at the same time conveying it''s message.  You can see the flyer further down the page.', 'Manchester Lifting Equipment Company', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'brannding-logo-website-design', '', '', '2018-03-15 18:06:07', '2018-03-15 18:06:07', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=websites&#038;p=155', 19, 'website', '', 0),
