(283, 1, '2013-02-03 21:43:04', '2013-02-03 21:43:04', 'I really enjoyed working with Nicola. Communication was flowing between us and I consider it essential when it comes to website design. Creating a website is a process, and in order for it to proceed smoothly you need to co-operate with your designer (being able to have a laugh trying ideas helps as well ..!). Before I decided to join forces with Nicola on my demanding new project, I had had a bad experience and wasted a considerable amount of time working on my website with a big, well-known, national organisation. They could not provide what I needed (nor assess my needs properly),e.g. a form where clients could upload their documents or ‘change the language’ button essential in this line of business for a group of my target clients. Nicola listened and delivered what I wanted, was quick to respond (very important!) and I learnt as we went along. She also made a logo for me by incorporating and polishing my visual concepts.\n\nWhat is more, she showed me how to amend my website in WordPress – very convenient and time-saving! It is easily done so I do not have to worry I will have to chase Nicola in the future if I need to add or amend something.  I can quickly do it myself with a couple of clicks – whether it is a comma missing or whether I fancy adding another image!\n\nFinal result: I now have a professional, functional, aesthetically pleasing and fully bi-lingual website my colleagues and clients compliment me on. Diligent perfectionist (as Nicola probably found out), I do not bestow praise easily. So well done and thank you!\n\nKasia Terry MA, Dip. Trans, LLB Law (Director – PEN Translations)', 'Kasia Terry', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'testimonial-by-kasia-terry-ma-dip-trans-llb-law-director-pen-translations', '', '', '2013-02-03 21:43:04', '2013-02-03 21:43:04', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=testimonial&amp;p=283', 0, 'testimonial', '', 0),
(285, 1, '2012-10-16 21:49:26', '2012-10-16 21:49:26', 'Being a new business we wanted to try and create an impact from day one. This brief was given to Nicola along with designing our logo which could be transferred onto our letter heads and business cards.\n\nWe think Nicola achieved this, and at a reasonable cost!\n\nIn fact we wil be using Nicola''s services again in the near future to update our website.\n\nWe have no hesitation in recommending Nicola for any web design work.', 'Steve Banks', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'steve-banks-lifting-inspection-services-ltd', '', '', '2012-10-16 21:49:26', '2012-10-16 21:49:26', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=testimonial&amp;p=285', 0, 'testimonial', '', 0),
(286, 1, '2013-01-06 21:51:25', '2013-01-06 21:51:25', 'I contacted Nicola after hearing about her through a friend who’d also had a website built by her. I had already tried a couple of large web design companies and been scared off by their production line approach to website design.\n\nI met with Nicola to discuss my requirements and she was both professional and efficient in offering her ideas as well as listening to my own requirements. Once she had a basic outline of the site she got started. The thing that impressed me most was Nicolas willingness to involve me at each stage of the build and how the site was built keeping tightly to my instructions. This would only be possible with a bespoke service such as the one Nicola offers.\n\nI needed a site to display my landscape photography. I also sell my prints and photography workshops through the site so it needed to be easy to use and navigate while at the same time displaying my work effectively. Nicola managed to achieve this in excess of my expectations.\n\nThe site has been very well received and it is also now ranking at the top for Google search terms which we identified beforehand.\n\nMoving on, little improvements and unforeseen changes have meant that the site has needed some additions to keep up with my changing business and Nicola has been great at tweaking and adding new features as they are needed.\n\nAll in all, a fast friendly service with much attention to detail at an affordable price.\n\n<a title="www.davidspeightphotography.com" href="http://www.davidspeightphotography.com" target="_blank">www.davidspeightphotography.com</a>', 'David Speight', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'david-speight', '', '', '2013-01-06 21:51:25', '2013-01-06 21:51:25', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=testimonial&amp;p=286', 0, 'testimonial', '', 0),
(298, 1, '2012-10-08 20:43:26', '2012-10-08 20:43:26', '<p>Nicola helped developed our sexual health website (<a href="http://www.trinitycentre.nhs.uk/">http://www.trinitycentre.nhs.uk/</a>)</p>\n<p>She was creative, realistic and suggested many ideas to help improve the website design.</p>', 'Kimberley Meleschko', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'kimberley-meleschko', '', '', '2012-10-08 20:43:26', '2012-10-08 20:43:26', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=testimonial&amp;p=298', 0, 'testimonial', '', 0),
