(318, 1, '2013-02-15 21:17:11', '2013-02-15 21:17:11', '<p>Hi Nicola,</p>\n<p>I just wanted to express my thanks for all your hard work in creating my website.  It looks fantastic! </p>\n<p>I know I kept changing my mind about all sorts of things but I''m so glad you just took it all on board and kept offering your own ideas as well as building it and making it work.</p>\n<p>And the cost was pretty reasonable too- I had some quotes that were quite a bit dearer but you have done everything I wanted- and with a smile!</p>\n<p>It was a pleasure working with you and I shall definitely pass on your details to any of my colleagues or friends who require a website creating.    </p>\n<p>Regards </p>\n<p>Richard</p>\n<p>(Richard Smith Tiling) </p>', 'Richard Smith', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'richard-smith', '', '', '2013-02-15 21:17:11', '2013-02-15 21:17:11', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=testimonial&amp;p=318', 0, 'testimonial', '', 0),
(320, 1, '2013-02-21 19:07:39', '2013-02-21 19:07:39', '<p>Yes.  If you are happy with your website but maybe just want some minor updates, e.g. add, remove or edit some text, add a new image, add a new page, adding social networking icons, e.g. facebook like buttons, then I can do this for you.  I will give you a quote for the work based on how long I expect it will take me.  Send me an email via my <a title="Contact" href="http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/contact/">contact page</a>.</p>', 'Can you make some changes to my existing website?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'can-you-make-some-changes-to-my-existing-website', '', '', '2013-02-21 19:07:39', '2013-02-21 19:07:39', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=faq&amp;p=320', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
(321, 1, '2013-02-21 19:13:40', '2013-02-21 19:13:40', 'Wordpress is a content management system.  "What does this mean?" I hear you cry!  Well it means that you can manage all your own content on your website, so you can edit all the text and images, and add new pages, reorder the menu, and loads more, all in an easy to use system.  You don''t have to email me whenever you want to edit some text or add an image.\r\n\r\nThis website is in Wordpress.  In fact below is a screenshot of this actual page in the in wordpress.  You can see where all the text is like on this page, and also all the icons similar to word, so you have bold, italics etc.  It''s really easy to use, and puts you in control.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class="alignnone wp-image-798 size-large" src="http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk//wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Screen-Shot-2017-06-04-at-21.00.12-1024x518.png" width="1024" height="518" />', 'What is Wordpress?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'what-is-wordpress', '', '', '2017-06-04 20:00:45', '2017-06-04 20:00:45', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=faq&#038;p=321', 0, 'faq', '', 0),
