(360, 1, '2013-04-22 19:51:09', '2013-04-22 19:51:09', '<p>Nicola completed a booking form for one of my clients, she supplied the files quickly and efficiently. She did an expert job and if I need any code work in the future I will be contacting her straight away.</p>\n<p>Brian Watson<br />Website designer/developer <br />Business Kick</p>', 'Brian Watson, Business Kick', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'brian-watson-business-kick', '', '', '2013-04-22 19:51:09', '2013-04-22 19:51:09', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=testimonial&amp;p=360', 0, 'testimonial', '', 0),
(363, 1, '2013-05-02 20:50:46', '2013-05-02 20:50:46', 'This project was for an auto-electrician in Huddersfield.  They already had a website that they had built with 1and1 hosting, but wanted something with a more streamlined feel, that incorporated their logo.\r\n\r\nI based the design of the site on their logo.  The logo was black and orange, so I reflected this colour scheme in the rest of the site design.  One of the things I pointed out to them on their old site was that it wasn''t immediately clear what they did, on landing on their homepage.  Bearing this in mind, I worked with Autolec HD to create a more streamlined structure, with all their services listed on one page.  Each service they provide has it''s own page, for clarity to the viewer and for SEO (search engine optimisation) purposes.  I also made sure with the design of the homepage that it was immediately clear that this was an auto electrician, by using design principles and carefully named section headings.\r\n\r\nAutolec HD needed some images for their website.  So I arranged to take some with my dSLR at their premises.  I got a great shot of them both smiling naturally, have a look at their <a href="http://autolechd.co.uk/about-us/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">about page</a>.', 'Autolec HD, Car Electrician', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'autolec-hd-car-electrician', '', '', '2018-03-15 18:17:12', '2018-03-15 18:17:12', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=websites&#038;p=363', 6, 'website', '', 0),
