(371, 1, '2013-05-14 19:34:51', '2013-05-14 19:34:51', '<p>Nicola recently updated and improved my website for holiday accommodation. She produced a site that was very attractive and pleasing to look at. It was easy to use and navigate to find out information. Nicola helped me understand how to use keywords to optimise Google searches and how to edit the site to keep it up to date. Communication was good. Nicola listened to what I wanted from the site, gave me good ideas of her own and persevered with minor teething problems until they were sorted. She was good value for money and I would have no hesitation in recommending her to others.</p>\n<p>Jean Parker</p>', 'Branscombe Holiday Let', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'branscombe-holiday-let', '', '', '2013-05-14 19:34:51', '2013-05-14 19:34:51', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=testimonial&amp;p=371', 0, 'testimonial', '', 0);
