(397, 1, '2013-07-05 22:53:10', '2013-07-05 22:53:10', '<p>My client organised a local walking group in Meltham, near Holmfirth.  He organised walks and wanted a website to promote these walks and for people to find out all the information about each walk.  There was a lot of functionality with this site.  It had to have news posts; it had to have the ability to add walks with each walk be in different categories, e.g. strenuous, long walk, hilly, etc.  Each walk needed to have certain information about it such as the bus route to the walk starting place, facilities available and various downloadable files.  </p>\n<p>Meltham Walkers also needed to have a place to store information about the group, including minutes and agenda of meetings.  I created the functionality for my client to upload documents and set meeting dates for site visitors to refer to.</p>\n<p>The background image is of Meltham.  I thought it important to have the subject of the website, walking in Meltham, the background.  Its sets every page off.  My client took several pictures of Meltham and I worked with him to choose the one that was right for the website.</p>\n<p>My client is busy updating the website with all the walks, so it is a little empty now, but keep checking back to see what walks are available in Meltham!</p>', 'Meltham Walking Group', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'meltham-walking-group', '', '', '2018-03-15 18:05:40', '2018-03-15 18:05:40', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=websites&#038;p=397', 20, 'website', '', 0),
