(441, 1, '2013-08-02 22:34:06', '2013-08-02 22:34:06', '<p>My client already had a website but was finding it quite dated.  It had been set up 10 years or so before by her son.  She wanted the website to have a fresh feeling and to advertise her rooms.</p>\n<p>I designed a logo for my client, something I identified what sorely missing from the existing site.  It had no life, no identity.  Based on the colours in the logo, I then went on to design the rest of the site.  </p>\n<p>It was important that there was distinct call to actions on each page, for instance, on the homepage the most prominent feature is the book now button. </p>', 'Huddersfield B&B', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'huddersfield-bb', '', '', '2018-03-15 18:05:35', '2018-03-15 18:05:35', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=websites&#038;p=441', 16, 'website', '', 0),
