(448, 1, '2013-08-18 15:25:27', '2013-08-18 15:25:27', '<p>My client approached me needing a new website.  They didn''t have any branding or logo.  My first step was to establish the clients target customers - Quantity Surveyors and Estimators.  We then spoke about what these potential clients would be looking for in a website.  We worked out that the site''s main focus was to look professional whilst showcasing all the client''s previous work.  </p>\n<p>The design of the site came from the company''s name - sterling.  It make me think of coins, sterling silver, etc.  Based on this, I designed a silver effect for the heading on each page.  This also suited the brand identity of being professional and quality-driven.</p>\n<p>My client wanted the site to be colourful, in order to reflect the product he was offering- painting and decorating.  I achieved this by using a background image of colour swatches.</p>', 'Sterling Decorators', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'sterling-decorators', '', '', '2018-03-15 18:05:31', '2018-03-15 18:05:31', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=websites&#038;p=448', 9, 'website', '', 0),
