(465, 1, '2013-09-06 21:03:20', '2013-09-06 21:03:20', 'My client''s old website was built in flash.  Flash is a technology that is not search engine friendly, and doesn''t show up on mobiles.  So if you have a flash website, no one will be able to see it on their mobiles.\r\n\r\nMy client wanted a simple, uncluttered look, with the homepage being an advertisement for the band.  I redesigned their website to have a clean and elegant look.  The site showcases their performances and their imagery, giving a classy, well presented look and feel.', 'Chequers Band', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'chequers-band', '', '', '2018-03-15 18:02:14', '2018-03-15 18:02:14', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=websites&#038;p=465', 12, 'website', '', 0),
