(473, 1, '2013-09-17 21:27:29', '2013-09-17 21:27:29', 'My client was dissatisfied with his old website design.  The background was very dark which drowned out the photos.  He came to me wanting a fresh, bright website which let the photos, rather than the design, do the talking.  He also wanted the website to respond to different screen sizes, showing a different layout depending on if viewed on a smartphone, tablet or laptop.  The site needed to feature a prints section where people could buy a print through Paypal.\r\n\r\nI designed a very minimal website based around his logo.  The theme was black &amp; white.  It was contrast.  The black and white of the logo mirrored the contrast between the colour in the photos and the minimal white background.', 'E-Commerce Responsive Photography Site', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'e-commerce-responsive-photography-site', '', '', '2018-03-15 17:59:51', '2018-03-15 17:59:51', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=websites&#038;p=473', 5, 'website', '', 0),
