(538, 1, '2013-11-30 21:57:39', '2013-11-30 21:57:39', 'Genuine Carers contacted me needing a website, fast!  They had all the imagery and content ready for the website build, and had a really good logo.\r\n\r\nI took the blue &amp; the grey from their logo and replicated these colours across the site, to reinforce the brand and to invoke a sense of calmness.  To strengthen the brand identity, I manipulated the images provided using photoshop to make the carers the focus of the picture, the blue of her uniform worked great with the website''s colours.\r\n\r\nIt''s a simple, yet extremely effected design, which I am very pleased with.', 'Care Provider, Huddersfield', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'care-provider-huddersfield', '', '', '2018-03-15 17:43:36', '2018-03-15 17:43:36', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=websites&#038;p=538', 7, 'website', '', 0),
