(555, 1, '2014-01-24 15:53:18', '2014-01-24 15:53:18', '<p>My client wanted a strong brand to represent her microbiology business.  Through use of bold imagery and text, I created a stand out online identify.  </p>\n<p>FMS arranged to have professional photos taken which worked wonderfully with the site.  It''s hard to make a site look good without great pictures.</p>\n<p>I chose the petri dish as the background because of the contrasting colours, and knowing how it would make the site stand out and be memorable.</p>', 'Microbiology Website', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'microbiology-website', '', '', '2018-03-15 17:46:56', '2018-03-15 17:46:56', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=websites&#038;p=555', 21, 'website', '', 0),
