(579, 1, '2014-03-18 19:19:04', '2014-03-18 19:19:04', '<p>Nicola started work on my website 6 months ago and has stuck with me until it went live last week – that’s determination for you. What I really like is it’s ‘MY’ site &amp; I can easily change pictures, update text, generally evolve it to suit my changing business – and I’m a total novice. Behind that, Nicola has developed a solid framework site that is fast and looks great, one of my requirements was it had to be simple – but still it looks nothing like any other site. </p>\n<p>Quite frankly, Nicola’s work on this project is the best investment my business made in 2013. She has a keen eye for design as well as being a top notch web developer.</p>\n<p>Tim Potts</p>\n<p>Retail Designer</p>', 'Tim Potts, 360 Degree Design', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'tim-potts-360-degree-design', '', '', '2014-03-18 19:19:04', '2014-03-18 19:19:04', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=testimonial&amp;p=579', 0, 'testimonial', '', 0),
(581, 1, '2014-03-19 20:23:21', '2014-03-19 20:23:21', '<p>My client wanted a simple presence on the web.  Most people in his field knew he was, and he wanted to offer his services on a freelance basis.  He didn''t want too much content, so I suggested a simple one page website.  I made the focus of the site his picture, since most people would know he he was, and this familiarity would let them know they were on the right website.</p>', 'Intellectual Property Lawyer', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'intellectual-property-lawyer', '', '', '2018-03-15 17:45:28', '2018-03-15 17:45:28', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=websites&#038;p=581', 10, 'website', '', 0),
