(584, 1, '2014-05-31 14:52:24', '2014-05-31 14:52:24', 'XL Projects needed a website fast.  My client contacted me with an urgent request for a website.  They had all the content, but just needed a design to pull it altogether.  Their sister company Kelland already had a logo, so I suggested we use the same logo style as Kelland.  My client agreed.\r\n\r\nI was a bit flummoxed as to how I would make a site about Injection Moulding look pretty.  However I quickly did some designs in photoshop with the content my client had gave me, using the colours from the logo.  I was very pleased with the results.', 'Xl Projects, Factory Moulding Company', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'xl-projects-factory-moulding-company', '', '', '2018-03-15 17:35:18', '2018-03-15 17:35:18', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=websites&#038;p=584', 8, 'website', '', 0),
