(588, 1, '2014-05-31 15:15:00', '2014-05-31 15:15:00', '<p>Ipors Real Estate Ltd were struggling with their current website.  Clients just didn''t know what they did.  They also didn''t appreciate how dark the website was, with a black background and red boxes overlaid.</p>\n<p>Using the colours from the logo, I created them a bright, clean and uncluttered website.  It was important that it was easy to use as this was the shop window for their trading platform.  It had to be a good user experience.  </p>\n<p>The site is responsive.  This means that anyone viewing it on a mobile sees a different design and layout.  The menu becomes a tap to show, and the page content fits nicely into the browser window, with no need to scroll horizontally.</p>', 'British & Irish Property Insurance Responsive Website', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'british-irish-property-insurance-responsive-website', '', '', '2018-03-15 17:41:13', '2018-03-15 17:41:13', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=websites&#038;p=588', 1, 'website', '', 0),
