(597, 1, '2014-09-29 19:11:48', '2014-09-29 19:11:48', '<p>Pudsey computers sell and repair equipment.  They approached me wanting a site build for them that they could sell their products through.  </p>\n<p>I used Magento, an open source e-commerce platform to create their ecommerce website.  The site is proving popular, and they now have it set up in their shop, so customers can browse the stock online and buy online if they want.</p>\n<p>In today''s ever changing digital market, it was important that visitors were able to view the site on a mobile.  So I made sure the site was responsive and scaled down nicely when viewed on a smaller device, thus making it easier for customers to browse and make purchases.</p>', 'Pudsey Computers e-commerce website', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'pudsey-computers-e-commerce-website', '', '', '2018-03-15 17:40:55', '2018-03-15 17:40:55', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=websites&#038;p=597', 0, 'website', '', 0),
