(603, 1, '2014-09-29 19:16:58', '2014-09-29 19:16:58', 'I contacted Nicola to discuss the development of a website for what was then just a ‘work in progress’ idea that I had for a new business.  Nicola patiently worked with me and designed not only my website but logo too.  I was very impressed at how she was able to deliver a website that captured everything about the business that we had discussed.\r\n\r\nQuite simply, Nicola is an excellent web designer whose services I will certainly use again and therefore have not hesitation in recommending to others.\r\n\r\nThanks Nicola', 'Bridget Bridgett, Picsave', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bridget-bridgett-picsave', '', '', '2018-03-15 17:11:24', '2018-03-15 17:11:24', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=testimonial&#038;p=603', 0, 'testimonial', '', 0),
