(629, 1, '2015-03-26 22:44:11', '2015-03-26 22:44:11', '<p>My client already had a website but was being asked for £200 a year simply to be on the internet! I redesigns his website and charged him a one off fee.  All he had to pay then was his hosting and domain name renewal - approximately £40 a year.</p><p>With the site being a jewellery website, I wanted to give the feeling of prestige and class.  So I decided to go for a gold colour scheme.  The site is responsive, meaning it scales down to a different layout on mobiles.</p><p>My client was very pleased with the result and regularly updates it with new offers.</p>', 'Huddersfield Jewellery Firm', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'huddersfield-jewellery-firm', '', '', '2017-06-02 19:34:17', '2017-06-02 19:34:17', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=websites&#038;p=629', 0, 'website', '', 0),
