(814, 1, '2013-03-25 21:33:04', '2013-03-25 21:33:04', '<p>I’m more than happy to endorse your work. You have been a pleasure to work with and I am really pleased with the outcome. Your solution met all the criteria we set out for the site rebuild, and your eye for design added that final finishing touch. </p>\n<p>Thank again for your work on this project. </p>', 'Graham Moore', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'graham-moore', '', '', '2013-03-25 21:33:04', '2013-03-25 21:33:04', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=testimonial&amp;p=334', 0, 'testimonial', '', 0),
(815, 1, '2013-04-07 18:22:01', '2013-04-07 18:22:01', '<p>Already having an established website with a good Google ranking, I needed someone who could update the site whilst retaining the original content and code. Nicola was able to carry out the changes I required whilst adding some interesting features of her own. I found Nicola easy to work with and the cost to be reasonable, I would not hesitate to use your services again and will recommend you where I can, thanks Nicola.</p>', 'Andy Kerr', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'andy-kerr', '', '', '2013-04-07 18:22:01', '2013-04-07 18:22:01', '', 0, 'http://huddersfieldwebsitedesigner.co.uk/?post_type=testimonial&amp;p=349', 0, 'testimonial', '', 0),
